      "role": "user",
      "content": "self care feels like a joke. what's the point of taking a breath if it's just to fill a house that feels completely empty? everything just feels heavy and grey. i look at the bed and it's just... huge. it's like i'm already a ghost just walking through these rooms. i don't see how things ever get better than this.",
